Syntax: politics

Displays the current political relationships (diplomacy) between all active
clans in the game. The output is a matrix showing every clan's standing
toward every other clan.

Diplomacy levels from most hostile to most friendly:
  WAR      -- Open warfare declared between the clans.
  HATRED   -- Deep enmity; hostility just short of formal war.
  DISLIKE  -- Unfriendly relations; distrust and friction.
  NEUTRAL  -- No formal relationship; indifference.
  RESPECT  -- Positive regard; cooperative but not allied.
  TRUST    -- Strong positive relations; reliable partnership.
  ALLY     -- Full alliance; clans act in each other's interests.

Players with the Diplomat flag will also see pending diplomacy change
requests from other clans.

